Titolo: Bomberman Live

Anno: 2007

Descrizione: Bomberman Live is a downloadable video game for the Xbox Live Arcade, developed by Backbone Entertainment as part of the Bomberman franchise. The game was announced on May 16, 2007 and released on July 18, 2007. It would later see a retail release as part of the 2009 Xbox Live Arcade Game Pack. 
A sequel, Bomberman Live: Battlefest, was released in 2010.